data.description: This charming 2nd floor condo in 55+ Lake Lawn is waiting for new owners. Features include a very bright open floor plan with foyer, great room, dining area, inside laundry with full size washer & dryer. Kitchen has tile floors, white cabinets, tile back splash, dome ceiling with fan. The air conditioned glass enclosed porch is a perfect place to relax and enjoy the beautiful view of the lake. 2 bedrooms and 2 baths and the spacious owners bedroom has lots of closets and the shower has been redone. Additional finishing touches are new microwave, electric hurricane shutters, air conditioner is 3 years old, new windows, new paint, carpet was just cleaned and a screened front entry. Complex has community pool and clubhouse, low HOA fees, and is very well maintained. Nestled in a fantastic location close to beaches, airport, shopping, golf courses, baseball stadiums, entertainment, and medical facilities. Enjoy carefree living in paradise.
